	“10 Ways Enterprise Mobility can Transform Government”
	"Clearly, enterprise mobility is transforming government. A recent survey by the Center for Digital Government (CDG) reveals the cost benefits and service enhancements that mobile technology is now delivering to public service organizations. The survey queried 450 public sector stakeholders from around the world on the topic of enterprise mobility."
	When it comes to benefits of mGov- between 72-95% of public sector stake holder agree with: 
* MGov improves G2C-relationsships (95%)
* Reduces costs (85%)
* Boost employee satisfaction and safety (90%)
* Improve productivity (90%)
* Advance transportation (80%)
* (Bolster public safety (73%))
* Improve public health (85%)
* Enhance education (93%)
* Speed up service delivery (72%)
	http://www.slideshare.net/sapmobile/cdg-infographic-mobilepublicsectorfinal


	The Center for Digital Government is a national research and advisory institute on information technology policies and best practices in state and local government. It’s a division of e.Republic
